    <title>2023-数据库课设-环境搭建-nginx</title>
    <link href="/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-nginx/"/>
    <url>/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-nginx/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h2><p>托管网页，把网页发给用户的浏览器等功能</p><p>默认端口 80</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>Session</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Shell">sudo apt update<br>sudo apt upgrade<br>sudo apt install nginx<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看运行状态</p><figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>Session</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Shell">sudo systemctl status nginx<br>ss -ntl <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-nginx/nginx.png"></p><p>有一个 80 端口</p><p><img src="/2023/06/19/2023-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E8%AF%BE%E8%AE%BE-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-nginx/port.png"></p><h2 id="远程连接"><a href="#远程连接" class="headerlink" title="远程连接"></a>远程连接</h2><p>默认远程连接</p><h2 id="服务器端口开放"><a href="#服务器端口开放" class="headerlink" title="服务器端口开放"></a>服务器端口开放</h2><p>默认 80 已经开放不用弄了</p>]]></content>
    
    
